title: StarTalk Live! Satisfying our Curiosity about Mars
description: StarTalk Live descends on The Bell House to celebrate the landing of the Curiosity Rover on Mars, with Neil deGrasse Tyson, Sarah Silverman, Jim Gaffigan, Eugene Mirman and Dr. David Grinspoon.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
